{"tid":2058970,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓政府將檢控兩個脫北者團體","createTime":"2020-06-10T14:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T14:17:27.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"80757e18af5f33b5132155a1bcecbfa81408a38f","tid":2058970,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:17:27.000Z","msg":"南韓統一部稱，除了向檢方舉報脫北者團體製造兩韓緊張形勢，及危害邊境地區居民安全的行為，亦會撤銷它們的營運許可。<br />\n<br />\n北韓因為不滿南韓縱容脫北者的反朝活動，周二起中斷兩韓所有聯絡渠道，並將對韓工作全面轉換為對敵工作。南韓當局低調回應引起在野黨派批評，統一部則反駁，稱對朝事務不可以感情用事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=393959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393959&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=01c037c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393959&h=4f270d01\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=393959</a>"}]}